reviewText: It's good, but pretty easy to do.
Super fast shipping and great quality! The workout is amazing! Even though they are a few years old the  pilates moves do not change.
I think this video really delivers and I will be using it 3-4x/week for toning and strength! This is not for beginners, though and YOU should definitely start with an easier one

I received my Malibu Pilates Perfect 10 workout DVD in a reasonable time. It came undamaged. I watched the video and it ran fine. I really enjoy the workout. It was a good purchase. Thank you Barb GreskoMalibu Pilates - High Intensity Series - Perfect 10's - Abs, Buns, Thighs
